result.longName: AS Siguldas Ciltslietu Un Maksligas Apseklosanas Stacija

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: AS Siguldas Ciltslietu Un Maksligas Apseklosanas Stacija produces and supplies breeding bull semen in the Republic of Latvia. The company also provides milk testing services; and other breeding related services, such as consultations on issues of cattle breeding, feeding and keeping, evaluation of cow exterior, artificial insemination of cows, and initial processing of the supervisory data. In addition, it provides milk making analysis and milk recording data processing services, as well as engages in animal breeding activities. The company was founded in 1957 and is based in Sigulda, the Republic of Latvia.
